/* Replaces lit/blinking icons with the unlit version. By default this only affects the GNS button. If you wish to replace any of the other buttons, remove the comment marks (slashes and asterisks) from the beginning (just before "img .." and end of each code block. Refer to the Flashnews block as an example - don't remove the comment marks around the title ( Flashnews, Darkness Message, etc.)

If you wish to re-enable the blinking/lit icons for any button, simply replace the comment marks. */


